{
  "section_id": "26-dive-into-deepseek-r1-single-n",
  "title": "Dive into DeepSeek R1 Single Node Results",
  "title_translation": "DeepSeek R1 单节点结果深度解析",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "id": "p000",
      "index": 0,
      "source": "On DeepSeek R1 FP8 1k1k, we see that MI355X is competitive with its counterpart B200 on single node scenarios, despite getting mogged on FP4 multi node scenarios. MI355X (SGLang) even beats B200 (SGLang) in throughput performance at lower interactivity levels. Moreover, MI355X (SGLang) beats B200 (TRT and SGLang) in most cases from a perf/TCO perspective.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0321",
      "parent_block_index": 321,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "On DeepSeek R1 FP8 1k1k, we see that MI355X is competitive with its counterpart B200 on single node scenarios, despite getting mogged on FP4 multi node scenarios. MI355X (SGLang) even beats B200 (SGLang) in throughput performance at lower interactivity levels. Moreover, MI355X (SGLang) beats B200 (TRT and SGLang) in most cases from a perf/TCO perspective.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "On DeepSeek R1 FP8 1k1k, we see that MI355X is competitive with its counterpart B200 on single node scenarios, despite getting mogged on FP4 multi node scenarios. MI355X (SGLang) even beats B200 (SGLang) in throughput performance at lower interactivity levels. Moreover, MI355X (SGLang) beats B200 (TRT and SGLang) in most cases from a perf/TCO perspective.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
      "segment_start": 0,
      "segment_end": 357,
      "expected_tokens": [],
      "format_recovery_status": "not_applicable",
      "format_errors": [],
      "is_heading": false,
      "heading_level": null,
      "heading_chain": [],
      "is_metadata": false,
      "metadata_type": null,
      "translations": {
        "pro": {
          "text": "在 DeepSeek R1 FP8 1k1k 负载下，我们发现 MI355X 在单节点场景中与竞品 B200 旗鼓相当，尽管其在 FP4 多节点场景下被全方位碾压。在较低的交互性下，MI355X (SGLang) 的吞吐量性能甚至反超了 B200 (SGLang)。此外，从性能与 TCO 的维度来看，MI355X (SGLang) 在大多数情况下都击败了 B200（无论是运行 TRT 还是 SGLang）。",
          "model": "pro",
          "created_at": "2026-04-08T01:09:06.553324",
          "tokenized_text": null,
          "format_issues": []
        }
      },
      "confirmed": null,
      "confirmed_tokenized": null,
      "confirmed_format_issues": [],
      "status": "translated",
      "ai_insight": {
        "overall_score": 9.524999999999999,
        "is_excellent": true,
        "applied_terms": [],
        "style": "专业技术",
        "steps": {
          "understand": true,
          "translate": true,
          "reflect": true,
          "refine": false
        },
        "understanding": {
          "role_in_article": "待分析",
          "relation_to_previous": "",
          "relation_to_next": "",
          "key_points": [],
          "translation_notes": []
        },
        "scores": {
          "readability": 9.5,
          "accuracy": 9.0
        },
        "issues": [
          {
            "type": "accuracy|terminology",
            "description": "原文的“perf/TCO”指的是性能与总拥有成本的比值（即单位成本带来的性能，或广义的性价比），而译文“性能与 TCO 的维度”容易被理解为“性能”和“TCO”两个独立的考量维度，削弱了该指标的复合比例属性。"
          },
          {
            "type": "accuracy|data",
            "description": "上一句对比的是 H200 与 MI325X，下一句却突然给出了 MI325X 和 B200 的数据采集时间。这极大概率是原文作者的笔误（将 H200 误写成了 B200）。译文虽然忠实于原文，但可能会让硬核读者产生困惑。"
          }
        ]
      },
      "history": []
    },
    {
      "id": "p001",
      "index": 1,
      "source": "Unfortunately, the year is 2026, and most frontier labs and inference providers are not running FP8 nor single node inference.",
