      "id": "p010",
      "index": 10,
      "source": "In comparing DeepSeek R1 FP8 perf between H200 (SGLang) and MI325X (SGLang), not much has changed since our initial release of InferenceXv1 last October. The MI325X data was captured on Feb 12th, 2026 with SGLang 0.5.8 whereas the B200 data was captured Jan 23, 2026 with SGLang 0.5.7.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
