    {
      "id": "p011",
      "index": 11,
      "source": "One thing we note is the considerably smaller interactivity range for MI325X than H200, with H200 ranging from 30-90 tok/sec/user whereas MI325X ranges from only 13-35 tok/sec/user. This is problematic for providers who would like to serve users at a broader range of interactivity.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
